tournaments.name: Offline Chat Achievement Hunt
tournaments.description: This 'tournament' is an event where teams have 9 days (including two weekends) to complete as many achievements as possible; achievements are *not* osu medals, but are listed on the site and include a range of explicit tasks, clue-based puzzles, and even other types. Point system is cumulative across all achievements and based on the number of other teams that complete the same achievement.

tournaments.description: 4v4 TS5-7 player-tiered tournament with three separate rank restrictions. Tier 1 (1 player): 1-infinity. Tier 2 (1 player): 3k-infinity. Tier 3 (3-5 players): 10k-infinity. Also some other tiering rules for matches.
